-- Chesapeake says it is not for sale: memo
-- 
-- Tue Jan 29, 2013 11:21pm EST
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2013/01/30/us-chesapeake-sale-idUSBRE90S17520130130

 

 HOUSTON  (Reuters) - The departure of Chief Executive Aubrey McClendon is not an indication that Chesapeake Energy Corp is up for sale, according to an email to sent to employees on Wednesday. 
 "...the company is not for sale," Chairman Archie Dunham wrote. Dunham also said the Chesapeake's board has set a drilling and completion budget of $6 billion. Chesapeake said McClendon will step down on April 1. (Reporting By  Anna Driver ; editing by Carol Bishopric)